name: FunMe
0:
”Alexa, Open Fun Me”
”Tell a joke Tom”
”Next Tom”
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fun me
des: Fun Me lights up your day with funny Chuck Norris jokes, but replaces the phrase "Chuck Norris" with yours!. Just say "Alexa, ask Fun Me for a joke" and then say your name.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
